description:
"Bishoujo Battle: Double Strike!" includes the two games;

- Bishoujo Battle: Mahjong Solitaire - Let the military girls of "Rikku G Earth" be your companions as classic tile-matching gets more exhilarating than ever!

- Bishoujo Battle: Cyber Panic - Inspired by the naughty back-room arcades of '90s Japan, Bishoujo Battle Cyber Panic! Start each action-packed stage with a silhouetted girl behind the playfield and dodge enemies while drawing lines that cut away when connected, methodically uncovering the image underneath.
